{% extends 'layout.html.twig' %}

{% set title = 'Hall of fame' %}

{% block meta_description %}View top performers and leaderboards for Quizstack's web development quizzes across all programming topics and difficulty levels{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

    {{ include('partials/banner.html.twig', {'color': 'gold'}) }}

    <div class="wrapper wrapper-large">
        <div class="page-header-container subtitle">
            <h1 class="big-title grow">Hall of fame</h1>
            <h2 class="fade-in-up md:text-lg opacity-75" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
                Compete weekly, monthly, or all-time and showcase your skills
            </h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wrapper wrapper-large">
        <div class="buttons-container mb-spacing-primary justify-end">
            <div class="radio-input-container scores">
                <ul class="switch glass box">
                    <li>
                        <button class="switch-label active">All time</button>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <button class="switch-label">Monthly</button>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <button class="switch-label">Weekly</button>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <ul data-period="all-time"
            class="score-container w-full grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-spacing-primary">
            {% for score in allTimeScores %}
                {% set period = 'all-time' %}
                {{ include('partials/scores-grid.html.twig', {'period': period}) }}
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>

        <ul data-period="month"
            class="score-container w-full grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-spacing-primary">
            {% for score in monthlyScores %}
                {% set period = 'month' %}
                {{ include('partials/scores-grid.html.twig', {'period': period}) }}
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>

        <ul data-period="week"
            class="score-container w-full grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-spacing-primary">
            {% for score in weeklyScores %}
                {% set period = 'week' %}
                {{ include('partials/scores-grid.html.twig', {'period': period}) }}
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="wrapper wrapper-large">
        <div class="pt-spacing-very-large-tertiary flex flex-col gap-4">
            <p class="fade-in-up opacity-75" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">Welcome to the Hall of Fame - where top
                performers earn recognition for consistent, high-quality play. Browse leaderboards by week, month, or
                all time to see who’s mastering HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Node.js, accessibility, performance,
                testing, and more. Each ranking reflects points earned from correct answers, speed, difficulty, and
                streak multipliers, rewarding both accuracy and momentum.</p>
            <p class="fade-in-up opacity-75" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">Sign in to track your position, compare
                with friends, and follow rivals. Build streaks, unlock badges, and aim for higher tiers, from Code
                Apprentice to Development Legend. Filters let you view global leaders or narrow results by topic and
                difficulty, so you can target your next breakthrough. Check back often - leaderboards reset
                weekly and monthly, offering fresh chances to rise. Learn from the best and turn every session into
                measurable
                progress.</p>
            <p class="fade-in-up opacity-75" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">Want your name on the board ? Practice with
                intent. Use Filters to focus on topics you’re weakest in, review missed questions, and revisit
                explanations from top commenters on the Activity page. Short daily sessions compound quickly—aim for
                consistent streaks, pace your attempts to maintain accuracy, and tackle higher - difficulty quizzes when
                you’re ready for bigger multipliers. Compete solo or create a team to combine scores and unlock special
                team badges.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

{% endblock %}